  "original_title": "\u2018\u201821 \u0db6\u0dbd\u0dcf\u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0ddc\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dd6 \u0d86\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dda \u0d91\u0d9a\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd9\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2\u2018\u2018",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"21 is not what you expected.\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former President Maithripala Sirisena, the Chairman of the Sri Lanka Freedom Party (SLFP) said today (1) that although the government is trying to bring in the 21st amendment and clean it up, it is not the amendment that the people expected.",
        "The former president said that it is completely different from the 19th amendment and said that it has given the current president the powers of the 20th constitutional amendment as well as other powers until the end of his tenure, and he hopes to submit amendments to it at the time of the committee.",
        "He also said that due to the wrong political, economic and social management of the present government, the country has gone back 70 to 80 years and is in a position to carry out home births.",
        "The former president also said that the government was not yet ready to rectify the mistakes made by appointing incompetents.",
        "Mr. Sirisena also said that all slogans, including national security, which was the main slogan of the Sri Lanka People's Front during the last election period, have now been canceled.",
        "The former president said this while addressing a press conference held at the Sri Lanka Freedom Party headquarters at Darley Road, Colombo."
      ],
